# Stock Broker Frontend - Netlify & Local Environment Variables

# The URL of your deployed Spring Boot backend API.
# During local development, leave this empty/commented out to use the local Vite proxy pointing to localhost:8081.
# When deploying to Netlify, set this variable in the Netlify dashboard under Site Settings -> Environment Variables.
# Example: VITE_API_URL=https://your-backend-api-url.onrender.com
VITE_API_URL=
